flowchart TB
  S([Run central setup]) --> ROOT{Root + Ubuntu?}
  ROOT -->|no| FAIL([Abort])
  ROOT -->|yes| BASE[Fix apt sources + install base utils]
  BASE --> IP[Detect local IP -> reuse as bind/connect address]
  IP --> ES[Install Elasticsearch + security + CA]
  ES --> KB[Install Kibana]
  KB --> WAZ[Install Wazuh Manager + API]
  WAZ --> SUR[Install Suricata + EVE]
  SUR --> FAL[Install Falco + Falcosidekick]
  FAL --> FB[Install + configure Filebeat]
  FB --> TG[Install + configure Telegraf]
  TG --> RDS[Install Redis]
  RDS --> HARD[Harden: firewall + SSH + restricted ports]
  HARD --> CHK{All services active?}
  CHK -->|no| LOGS[Show logs + retry] --> CHK
  CHK -->|yes| VER[Verify telemetry in Elasticsearch]
  VER --> SUM([Print setup summary])
